with expected_protocol(ik.hp.HP3456a, ['HO0T4SO1', 'RER', 'REY', 'REZ',
    'W600.0STR', 'W1.0STY', 'W0.1055STZ'], ['+0600.000E+0', '+1.000000E+0',
    '+105.5000E-3'], sep='\r') as dmm:
    assert dmm.r == +600.0
    assert dmm.y == +1.0
    assert dmm.z == +0.1055
    dmm.r = +600.0
    dmm.y = +1.0
    dmm.z = +0.1055
